Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"North Block"\N"West Block" "South Block" "East Block"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings of those who are in anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are crushed by a dry cloud of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who seek hope,\Nand those who cling to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their feelings cross each other,\Nuncertain what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,marking an era of history ending in sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami engaged in mortal combat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Miss Doublefinger,\Nwho has Spike Spike Fruit powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was overwhelmingly dominated by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Usopp's invention, the Clima Takt,\Ngradually began to show it's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Crocodile appeared at the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally began to reveal the\Nultimate goal behind his ambitions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of Vivi and Cobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Secret Passed Down in the Royal Family!\NThe Ancient Weapon Pluton"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about?\NWhat's Pluton? What on earth is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that one shot from Pluton\Nwill completely destroy an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's most disastrous weapon\Nfrom ancient times, also called a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be sleeping\Nsomewhere in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient weapon? Such a\Nthing exists in this country...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Father knew about it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret passed down with the throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's been my goal from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it, I'll be able to build\Nthe best military state right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve that,\Nall this time you've been...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I become the king of this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's easy to bring pirates in\Nthis area under my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My influence will increase,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will eventually gain more power\Nthan even the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a dreamlike country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that the World\NGovernment would allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably wouldn't. That's why\NI need it... the powerful Pluton...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where on earth\Nyou heard that name,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know where it is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not even certain such a thing\Nreally exists somewhere in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What you say\Nprobably isn't a complete lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think that that was also possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know, too, that its\Nvery existence is in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What noisy flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Cobra-sama has\Nbeen crucified by Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Cobra-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do our utmost\Nto get inside somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't do anything because of\Nthose hands coming out from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible unless we do\Nsomething about those hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rebel army will reach that Square\Nwithin 20 minutes or so and start fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that... in other words,\Nat 4:30 pm, 30 minutes from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've ordered that a powerful\Ncannonball be shot into the Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a special shell that can destroy\Nanything within a 5 km diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The view from here will\Ncompletely change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one from either the royal army\Nor the rebel army will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the battle will be ceased forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy? After all,\Nyou wanted to stop them so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of doing things in a roundabout\Nway, like blowing up the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be quicker if we just\Ncompletely blow up both the armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth did they\Ndo to you to deserve it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You are... You are...\N--Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! What good will it do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Mr. Cobra. Let me\Nask you another question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find the Poneglyph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poneglyph... Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you where it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from a wise king,\NCobra. You're a clever man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... take this any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Nami. How you use the Clima Takt\Ncomes down to your head after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think frantically to survive the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our real weapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Balls and Cool Balls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is take full advantage of\Ntheir characteristics and combine them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power of the Clima Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one last thing... Tornado Tempo...!\NThis is the centerpiece of this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado Tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as your enemy is human, they\Nwon't be able to stand after being hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is the very last resort\Nand you only get one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss, consider it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss, it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you have\Nan interesting weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it doesn't have practical\Nattacks, isn't it just a toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever its purpose is,\Nyou can call it... a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when it can harm people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry up, I'll be killed...\NThe last powerful technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado Tempo... I have to do it now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give that back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill me with a toy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sweater can probably produce\Nbetter electricity than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know until I try! Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is get her to drop\Nher guard so that she can't dodge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this one-shot attack,\Nthe Tornado Tempo...! Maybe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that I can do by using
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three kinds of air bubbles and the\Nextremely dry weather of this country...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish there were at least a little\Nmore moisture in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moisture... That's right! If I remember\Ncorrectly, there's a rain technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water tricks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprinkler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're desperate, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. I've had\Nenough of your party tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is at its height. Let's call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea urchin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Urchin Stinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you Swiss cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'd call\NSwiss cheese! It's even burnt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In appreciation of your show earlier,\NI'll show you something interesting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance! Heat Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot air goes upwards\Nwhile absorbing moisture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it collides with cold air that's\Ndescending, it rapidly cools
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the moisture gets frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spike Spike Doping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said pay attention, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stinger Flail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... these wounds are nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's fighting with their very lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my arms get torn off\Nor my nose gets broken, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk too much,\Nyou'll cause internal bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're still alive for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd the battle with Mr. 2 turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! My goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took them back\Nfrom him! Thanks, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a... Ahh!\NHey, wait a sec! They're broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! This is the newest\Nmodel in the North Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how valuable\Nthese goggles are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the auxiliary\Nforce for the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there'll be more of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it. I guess Vivi-chan\Ncouldn't stop the rebel army...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Vaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where have you been hiding, Lashes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to the palace. We might\Nstill be able to help Vivi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--Hey, Usopp! Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...! Ah, hey, Lashes! Let me get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Can't you see these wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lashes! Stop! Let me get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, at least you're a first-class\Nexpert at running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! The air bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's formed! It's small, but it's still a cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough...! I'll let it grow more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stinger... Flail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you prepared to die yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bluffing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a fine day today\Nwith stable humidity and wind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as a high-pressure system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in one particular area, you\Nneed to watch for mirages and cyclones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be on the lookout for tornados.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tornado Tempo... This is the\Ncenterpiece of this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the very last resort\Nand you only get one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss, consider it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss, it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast is tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it work... the last attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since I wanted to fight with\Nmy own hands... for her...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san... Don't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try putting all of our\Nlives on the line together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can cry those kinds of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you actually hate this\Nand want to beat him up the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, it calls forth clouds...\Nother times, it makes rain fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet other times, it produces winds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The miraculous Clima Takt! I'll make it work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last powerful technique! For Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your left leg has taken lots of injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't actually keep\Nstanding any more, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Urchin Stinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... nothing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what\Npain she's going through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to her pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a leg or two, or three...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this... Tornado Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doves tangled up on me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it... I did it! Usopp... Vivi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - North Block"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:30.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - North Block"\N"Battle behind the Mehdi Assembly Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:38.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - North Block"\N"Battle behind the Mehdi Assembly Hall"\N"Winner: Nami"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember... your face...\NIt's in my fuzzy memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken, you were a famous\Nbounty hunter in the West Blue... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as an assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you fight for?\NYou're Crocodile's dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing it in order to at least get\Nsome nice scraps by licking his hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you... the difference in pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...between your swords and mine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull... Needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spider...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, your body is hard as steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I'm capable of cutting\Neven steel, I can't cut you down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smashing and cutting\Nattacks don't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm not yet capable of\Ncutting steel, I can't defeat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph... Then what're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll sympathize with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for a\Ndifficult situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that it's about\Ntime for me to go to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a man who can even cut steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even say half of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm by your side, I glitter\Nevery time we share a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smile you gently gave me\Nwas a very happy and kind one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glory glory you're my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here, even\Nthese tears turn to courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong,\NI want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll make it there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore on that day that\NI would never lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how large the wall standing\Nin front of me right now is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you can't even give me a scratch,\Nthere's only one way left for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do I lack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Secret of Powerful Swordplay! Ability to\NCut Steel and the Rhythm Things Have"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
